    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/tax-arrangements"/>
    <title>Public sector appointees: tax arrangements </title>
    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary>Review of tax arrangements of public sector appointees of MOD.</summary>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;On 23 May 2012, the government published a review of the tax arrangements of public sector appointees. The review identified the number of off payroll engagements worth more than £58,200 per annum across government and made recommendations to improve the tax transparency of these kind of arrangements. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The following document constitutes the &lt;abbr title="Ministry of Defence"&gt;MOD&lt;/abbr&gt;’s submission to this review.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
